data.meta_description: Images of Bill Birch's birthday parties held on March 1 of each year. This reel contains birthdays one through seven. Featured in the film are Harry Birch, Lucille Birch, William H. Horton, and Mrs. Horton. This film is a 16mm optical reduction from the original 35mm nitrate.
